(40, 23, 13, 55, 4, 15, 15, 'shut up the kingdom of heaven', 'Opposition to Spiritual Authority', 'This connection highlights the theme of opposition to spiritual authority. Both passages address individuals who hinder others from accessing truth or faith, with Matthew focusing on the Pharisees'' hypocrisy and Timothy warning against a person who withstood their words.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
